msgctxt "1680"
msgid "Hana"
msgstr "Hana"

msgctxt "1684"
msgid "Akiyama"
msgstr "Akiyama"

msgctxt "120_Hana"
msgid "I can't believe I'm going to karaoke with you, Chief...\\r\n"
"I'm so excited. Now, what should I sing?"
msgstr "No puedo creer que vaya al karaoke contigo, Jefe...\\r\n"
"Estoy tan emocionada. Ahora, ¿qué debería cantar?"

msgctxt "132_Hana"
msgid "Oh, I know! Why don't we sing a duet? You know how to sing \"Pure Love in Kamurocho,\" right, Chief!?"
msgstr "¡Oh, lo sé! ¿Por qué no cantamos un dueto? Sabes cantar \"Pure Love in Kamurocho\", ¿verdad, Jefe!?"

msgctxt "144_Hana"
msgid "Hehe... Don't you think we were completely in sync? We were flowing like pros."
msgstr "Jeje... ¿No crees que estábamos completamente sincronizados? Fluíamos como profesionales."

msgctxt "156_Akiyama"
msgid "Heheh, I guess so."
msgstr "Heheh, supongo que sí."

msgctxt "168_Hana"
msgid "Chief... Stop getting in my way."
msgstr "Jefe... Deje de meterse en mi camino."

msgctxt "180_Akiyama"
msgid "Sorry..."
msgstr "Lo siento..."

msgctxt "192_Hana"
msgid "That was perfect! I think we could release a CD. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Eso fue perfecto! Creo que podríamos lanzar un CD. <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "204_Akiyama"
msgid "Heheh, sure."
msgstr "Jejeje, claro."

